ules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5542:\"\n<p>We recently release QSM 6.3.0 with many changes, most notable are 2 big changes</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>UI Overhaul</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We are undergoing a much-needed massive UI overhaul. We have couple of goals in for this &#8211; good on eyes, ease of use and ease of navigation. Our first change in this direction is completely new Quiz and Survey index table.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-1-1024x584.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-63535\" srcset=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-1-1024x584.png 1024w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-1-300x171.png 300w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-1-768x438.png 768w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-1-1200x684.png 1200w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-1-375x214.png 375w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-1-760x433.png 760w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>New Look for Quizzes/Surveys</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Rich Answers</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most demanded feature! You can now create rich answers in your quizzes / surveys and put anything in there (well, limited to what WordPress allows).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-2-1024x608.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-63536\" srcset=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-2-1024x608.png 1024w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-2-300x178.png 300w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-2-768x456.png 768w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-2-375x223.png 375w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-2-760x452.png 760w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-update-2.png 1104w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>3 New Plugins!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We have launched three new plugins which were being demanded by the community. </p>\n\n\n\n<h4><a href=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/downloads/save-and-resume/\">Save and Resume</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Allow users to save or resume a quiz or survey where they left off. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-save-resume-1024x684.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-63537\" srcset=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-save-resume-1024x684.png 1024w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-save-resume-300x200.png 300w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-save-resume-768x513.png 768w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-save-resume-600x400.png 600w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-save-resume-1200x801.png 1200w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-save-resume-375x250.png 375w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-save-resume-760x508.png 760w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h4><a href=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/downloads/paypal-and-stripe-payment-integration/\">Payment Integration</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Enable Paypal or Stripe payments for a quiz or survey. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-payment-stripe-1024x561.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-63538\" srcset=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-payment-stripe-1024x561.png 1024w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-payment-stripe-300x164.png 300w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-payment-stripe-768x420.png 768w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-payment-stripe-1200x657.png 1200w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-payment-stripe-375x205.png 375w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/qsm-payment-stripe-760x416.png 760w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h4><a href=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/downloads/recaptcha\">reCaptcha</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Implement Google&#8217;s reCaptcha to block any bot attacks on your quiz and put a full stop to the spam problem.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/recaptcha-preview-1024x802.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-63539\" srcset=\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/recaptcha-preview-1024x802.png 1024w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/recaptcha-preview-300x235.png 300w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/recaptcha-preview-768x601.png 768w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/recaptcha-preview-375x294.png 375w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/recaptcha-preview-760x595.png 760w, https://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/recaptcha-preview.png 1114w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Price Drop on Bundle</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We have dropped the price on premium bundle to $99 and you can get an additional discount of 10% by using the code <strong>MAYDAY2019</strong>, this code will expire on 10th May 2019.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://quizandsu